Every buy or sell literally saves lives.


2. Origin & Vision (November–December 2025)
The movement began with a simple question:
“What if crypto could be the most powerful force for good the world has ever seen?” “People helping people helping people” became our mantra. Mr. Nibbles — a shelter dog in need of a forever home — became the emotional heartbeat of the project. From that single story, the vision rapidly expanded: save dogs, save kids, plant hope, and track every single impact on-chain so trust is never in question again.


