4. Tokenomics & Economic Engine (Self-Funding)
Fair launch on DEX only (Raydium, Uniswap, or Shibarium-native).
No presale. No team allocation. No VCs. 4% Buy / 4% Sell Tax (auto-split on every transaction): 
•	1% → Liquidity (auto-adds to pool forever) 
•	1% → Marketing & growth wallet 
•	1% → Treasury (direct on-chain funding for all programs) 
•	1% → Buyback & Burn + IRL Land/Sanctuary Fund
Burn Mechanism: Built-in deflation + impact. A portion of the 1% buyback automatically burns supply while the remainder funds physical land purchases for sanctuaries. FHE Zama Confidentiality Layer: Optional private donations and private balances while keeping all charity impact fully transparent and verifiable on-chain. Governance: Token holders vote on tax rates, program allocations, upgrades, and future direction.


